<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'home' %>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5; /* Set a light background color */
      color: #333; /* Set the text color */
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
   }



    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      color: #007bff; /* Set a primary color for headings */
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #666; /* Set a slightly muted text color */
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .welcome-message {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 1em;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .btn-dark {
      background-color: #343a40; /* Set a dark background color for dark buttons */
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1><em> Insightful Diary </em></h1>
  <p>Are you tired of the daily grind and don't know why? Here you can search certain phrases that relate to your current mood and get an article that gives you insightful details about it! After reading the article, you can jot down what you learned from it, how you felt after reading it, or whatever your heart desires!</p>

  <% if user_signed_in? %>
    <div class="welcome-message">üëãüèª Welcome, <%= current_user.first_name.capitalize %>!</div>
    <%= button_to "Sign out", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: "btn btn-dark" %>
  <% else %>
    <%= button_to "Sign in", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-dark" %>
  <% end %>
</body>
</html>

